1. Create folder Models in api
2. Create New C# file Post.cs in Models folder
3. Create New C# file Comment.cs in Models folder
4. Create Properties (prop+tab) in Post
        You are going to need an int Id, string Title, string Body, List<Comment> Comments = new List<Comment>();

5. Create Properties (prop+tab) in Comment
        You are going to need an Int Id, string Title, string Body
        We will also need to connect the Comment to the Post, include these Properties:
        public int? PostId { get; set; }
        //Navigation Property
        public Post? Post { get; set; }